Early Access Review

Despite a several games' clone I would have approved it for being a fun shooting piece with nicely animated futuristic background scenery and destructible landscape. I like the idea and the physics. But it has strong drawbacks:
1) Unity engine seems to be incapable of rendering fastpaced action and it lags like hell;
2) Levels are small and so similar in architecture;
3) Zero online in multiplayer shooter.

